1
00:01:40,519 --> 00:01:41,640
Lord Eunuch, please see the truth.

2
00:01:42,000 --> 00:01:43,760
I didn't see Lord Meng at all that day.

3
00:01:44,439 --> 00:01:45,760
He realized he was being followed.

4
00:01:46,120 --> 00:01:47,560
So he asked me to investigate.

5
00:01:48,359 --> 00:01:49,480
When I arrived,

6
00:01:49,480 --> 00:01:50,400
he was still meeting a guest.

7
00:01:50,920 --> 00:01:53,159
I thought I'd drink a cup of tea and wait for him.

8
00:01:54,040 --> 00:01:55,120
And guess what happened?

9
00:01:55,680 --> 00:01:56,599
After I finished that tea,

10
00:01:56,599 --> 00:01:57,719
I just passed out.

11
00:01:59,239 --> 00:02:02,280
So you're saying you were framed.

12
00:02:03,079 --> 00:02:04,159
Exactly.

13
00:02:05,359 --> 00:02:08,680
So you volunteered to come to the villa to investigate,

14
00:02:09,439 --> 00:02:10,840
in order to save yourself.

15
00:02:11,560 --> 00:02:12,400
Why else?

16
00:02:12,680 --> 00:02:14,199
Who wants to die if they can live?

17
00:02:16,400 --> 00:02:17,159
Lord Eunuch,

18
00:02:17,400 --> 00:02:19,960
do you know that day, that blade...

19
00:02:19,960 --> 00:02:21,280
was right here against my neck.

20
00:02:21,280 --> 00:02:21,800
Right here.

21
00:02:22,199 --> 00:02:23,639
I was this close to...

22
00:02:26,439 --> 00:02:28,639
Then you already know the solution to the secret treasure.

23
00:02:29,719 --> 00:02:31,000
I... don't know.

24
00:02:32,439 --> 00:02:32,960
Lord Eunuch,

25
00:02:33,360 --> 00:02:35,719
is there a connection between these two questions?

26
00:02:35,719 --> 00:02:36,639
Master Ye,

27
00:02:37,639 --> 00:02:39,280
you went to the Jingzhao Prefecture,

28
00:02:39,400 --> 00:02:40,680
and Lord Meng died.

29
00:02:41,120 --> 00:02:42,439
You came to this villa,

30
00:02:42,560 --> 00:02:43,719
and the Villa Master died.

31
00:02:43,840 --> 00:02:45,439
The guests died too.

32
00:02:46,280 --> 00:02:47,280
Master Ye,

33
00:02:47,919 --> 00:02:49,680
you are bad luck.

34
00:02:50,840 --> 00:02:51,400
Perhaps,

35
00:02:52,319 --> 00:02:53,439
it's not that I'm bad luck.

36
00:02:54,159 --> 00:02:55,800
But rather Heaven has opened its eyes,

37
00:02:57,159 --> 00:02:58,719
borrowing my righteousness

38
00:02:59,120 --> 00:03:00,599
to rid the people of evil.

39
00:03:06,199 --> 00:03:06,759
Men!

40
00:03:09,879 --> 00:03:10,360
Lord Eunuch!

41
00:03:10,560 --> 00:03:11,520
I haven't finished speaking!

42
00:03:12,240 --> 00:03:13,280
Listen to me chat a bit longer!

43
00:03:13,439 --> 00:03:14,000
Lord Eunuch!

44
00:03:14,759 --> 00:03:16,000
Listen to me for just a while longer!

45
00:03:23,400 --> 00:03:24,599
As for me,

46
00:03:24,840 --> 00:03:26,120
I can't stand the sight of blood.

47
00:03:27,439 --> 00:03:29,039
And I don't like beating around the bush.

48
00:03:29,639 --> 00:03:30,479
This medicine,

49
00:03:31,240 --> 00:03:33,120
is called the Heart-Devouring Pill.

50
00:03:33,439 --> 00:03:36,680
After taking it, it feels like ten thousand arrows piercing the heart.

51
00:03:36,680 --> 00:03:38,360
You will beg for life but cannot live,

52
00:03:38,360 --> 00:03:40,560
and beg for death but cannot die.

53
00:03:46,360 --> 00:03:47,599
Master Ye,

54
00:03:47,840 --> 00:03:49,319
let's keep it simple.

55
00:03:50,599 --> 00:03:52,400
You give me a satisfactory answer,

56
00:03:52,759 --> 00:03:53,879
and I will spare you.

57
00:03:55,039 --> 00:03:56,000
Otherwise,

58
00:03:56,199 --> 00:03:57,360
this antidote...

59
00:04:09,280 --> 00:04:09,960
The medicine is here.

60
00:04:13,280 --> 00:04:13,840
Drink it, quick.

61
00:04:21,759 --> 00:04:23,000
Ye Li is being tortured.

62
00:04:23,680 --> 00:04:24,240
Don't move.

63
00:04:24,439 --> 00:04:25,240
Self-preservation is what matters now.

64
00:04:29,279 --> 00:04:29,920
Don't look for trouble.

65
00:04:30,639 --> 00:04:31,920
If I only cared about self-preservation,

66
00:04:32,240 --> 00:04:33,839
I wouldn't have joined the Dali Temple.

67
00:04:34,120 --> 00:04:35,000
But if you don't recover,

68
00:04:35,199 --> 00:04:36,680
who here can beat them right now?

69
00:04:38,079 --> 00:04:39,199
I can't die here.

70
00:04:39,199 --> 00:04:40,240
I can't die here.

71
00:04:40,399 --> 00:04:41,319
I can't die here.

72
00:04:41,519 --> 00:04:42,439
I can't die here.

73
00:04:42,560 --> 00:04:43,279
I haven't taken a wife or had kids yet.

74
00:04:43,279 --> 00:04:44,519
Can you just shut up?

75
00:04:45,759 --> 00:04:46,839
I'm scared, okay?

76
00:04:47,759 --> 00:04:49,319
Just listen to Si-niang.

77
00:04:50,199 --> 00:04:51,120
That miracle doctor...

78
00:04:51,480 --> 00:04:51,800
No...

79
00:04:52,279 --> 00:04:53,120
Young Master Ye...

80
00:04:53,800 --> 00:04:56,800
is in a truly horrible state right now.

81
00:04:59,199 --> 00:05:00,160
This Lord Liu...

82
00:05:01,000 --> 00:05:02,600
to deceive everyone earlier,

83
00:05:03,519 --> 00:05:05,079
you pretended to be an honest man for so long.

84
00:05:05,319 --> 00:05:06,639
You must have felt so wronged.

85
00:05:07,199 --> 00:05:07,959
Keep talking nonsense,

86
00:05:09,040 --> 00:05:10,399
and you'll go join the Villa Master.

87
00:05:11,199 --> 00:05:12,639
Fine! Come on!

88
00:05:12,920 --> 00:05:13,720
Let go!

89
00:05:23,120 --> 00:05:24,439
Come at me if you have a problem!

90
00:05:25,439 --> 00:05:26,639
I'm not dead yet!

91
00:05:29,480 --> 00:05:30,079
Come on!

92
00:05:38,279 --> 00:05:39,279
I'll ask you again.

93
00:05:40,519 --> 00:05:41,879
Lord Meng's death...

94
00:05:42,480 --> 00:05:44,439
was entirely because you were dissatisfied with the Jingzhao Yin

95
00:05:44,439 --> 00:05:46,480
refusing to retry the old Zhao family case.

96
00:05:46,480 --> 00:05:48,000
You sought personal revenge.

97
00:05:48,560 --> 00:05:49,839
Is that true or not?

98
00:05:51,040 --> 00:05:51,920
No.

99
00:06:00,079 --> 00:06:02,439
I'll give you one last chance.

100
00:06:02,800 --> 00:06:03,480
The secret code.

101
00:06:04,360 --> 00:06:05,160
The confession.

102
00:06:06,319 --> 00:06:10,120
You must tell me one of them before dusk tomorrow.

103
00:06:12,199 --> 00:06:13,120
Otherwise,

104
00:06:15,439 --> 00:06:17,959
you will stay here forever.

105
00:06:34,000 --> 00:06:34,600
Ye Li.

106
00:06:34,839 --> 00:06:36,079
I've already fed you the antidote.

107
00:06:36,560 --> 00:06:37,439
Once the poison is neutralized,

108
00:06:37,639 --> 00:06:38,319
you'll be fine.

109
00:06:40,720 --> 00:06:41,519
Chaoyun.

110
00:06:49,240 --> 00:06:50,000
Chaoyun.

111
00:06:56,079 --> 00:06:56,759
Chaoyun.

112
00:06:59,279 --> 00:06:59,879
So cold.

113
00:07:01,399 --> 00:07:02,120
So cold.

114
00:07:03,959 --> 00:07:04,639
So cold.

115
00:07:05,600 --> 00:07:06,279
So cold.

116
00:07:07,839 --> 00:07:08,480
Cold.

117
00:07:27,319 --> 00:07:28,000
So cold.

118
00:07:33,560 --> 00:07:34,959
Ye Li.

119
00:07:35,839 --> 00:07:36,680
I'm taking you away.

120
00:07:42,560 --> 00:07:43,439
Chaoyun, don't be afraid, don't be afraid.

121
00:07:43,439 --> 00:07:44,600
Kill them. Leave no one alive.

122
00:07:44,600 --> 00:07:45,199
Yes!

123
00:07:48,959 --> 00:07:51,120
Chaoyun, we escaped.

124
00:07:53,399 --> 00:07:55,759
Ye Li, let's rest a bit.

125
00:08:01,319 --> 00:08:02,040
It hurts.

126
00:08:02,480 --> 00:08:03,160
Ye Li.

127
00:08:04,560 --> 00:08:05,600
I'm in so much pain.

128
00:08:06,800 --> 00:08:08,360
Chaoyun, you're hurt.

129
00:08:09,680 --> 00:08:10,480
Chaoyun.

130
00:08:16,319 --> 00:08:17,160
Chaoyun.

131
00:08:18,040 --> 00:08:18,680
Don't sleep.

132
00:08:20,439 --> 00:08:21,480
Let me see the wound.

133
00:08:37,399 --> 00:08:38,159
It won't hurt anymore.

134
00:08:38,679 --> 00:08:39,200
It won't hurt anymore.

135
00:08:39,200 --> 00:08:39,720
It hurts.

136
00:08:39,960 --> 00:08:40,919
It won't hurt, it won't hurt.

137
00:08:41,799 --> 00:08:42,360
It hurts.

138
00:08:58,320 --> 00:08:58,960
Don't be afraid.

139
00:08:59,720 --> 00:09:00,840
When the rain stops,

140
00:09:01,879 --> 00:09:03,000
we'll go home.

141
00:09:11,320 --> 00:09:11,960
Chaoyun.

142
00:09:18,919 --> 00:09:19,639
Chaoyun.

143
00:09:23,480 --> 00:09:24,360
Chaoyun.

144
00:09:28,159 --> 00:09:29,039
Ye Li.

145
00:09:33,000 --> 00:09:33,799
Ye Li.

146
00:09:37,960 --> 00:09:38,639
Chaoyun.

147
00:09:49,120 --> 00:09:50,120
Are you still cold?

148
00:09:57,000 --> 00:09:58,000
Drink the medicine first.

149
00:10:07,759 --> 00:10:08,600
Just now,

150
00:10:10,919 --> 00:10:11,720
I had a dream.

151
00:10:17,679 --> 00:10:18,440
In the dream,

152
00:10:20,600 --> 00:10:21,799
you kept calling out for Chaoyun.

153
00:10:34,720 --> 00:10:36,039
She is my childhood sweetheart.

154
00:10:36,679 --> 00:10:37,919
And the one I love.

155
00:10:42,120 --> 00:10:42,960
So,

156
00:10:44,639 --> 00:10:45,919
you think I look like her?

157
00:10:47,200 --> 00:10:47,720
I...

158
00:10:52,519 --> 00:10:53,600
You're still very weak.

159
00:10:53,960 --> 00:10:54,840
Let me help you lie down.

160
00:11:07,320 --> 00:11:08,080
Where are you going?

161
00:11:10,519 --> 00:11:11,759
Just get some sleep first.

162
00:11:44,639 --> 00:11:45,399
Miss.

163
00:11:45,519 --> 00:11:47,039
The rain is getting heavy. Let's go back.

164
00:11:49,000 --> 00:11:49,559
All right.

165
00:11:56,240 --> 00:11:56,919
I'm sorry.

166
00:11:58,080 --> 00:11:58,960
Who are you?

167
00:11:59,399 --> 00:12:00,799
How dare you trespass in my inner courtyard?

168
00:12:02,039 --> 00:12:02,960
I didn't trespass.

169
00:12:03,639 --> 00:12:04,679
I came with my father.

170
00:12:05,279 --> 00:12:06,080
My name is Ye Li.

171
00:12:06,519 --> 00:12:08,399
Ye for willow, Li for propriety.

172
00:12:10,240 --> 00:12:11,559
Ye Li.

173
00:12:18,039 --> 00:12:18,879
Um...

174
00:12:19,879 --> 00:12:20,679
You dropped your hairpin.

175
00:12:48,639 --> 00:12:53,039
Are you the son of Uncle Ye, the Vice Minister?

176
00:12:55,240 --> 00:12:55,840
Indeed.

177
00:12:56,519 --> 00:12:58,840
My father brought me to visit Lord Censor.

178
00:13:00,120 --> 00:13:01,720
I was careless

179
00:13:02,720 --> 00:13:03,840
and went the wrong way.

180
00:13:18,519 --> 00:13:19,600
Go through this hall,

181
00:13:19,919 --> 00:13:21,240
and you'll find your father.

182
00:13:24,320 --> 00:13:24,960
Many thanks.

183
00:13:33,360 --> 00:13:34,039
Take this.

184
00:13:35,240 --> 00:13:35,759
I...

185
00:13:38,879 --> 00:13:39,639
Miss!

186
00:13:46,039 --> 00:13:47,200
What is your name?

187
00:13:56,559 --> 00:13:57,679
Zhaoyun.
